c: 3
v: 151
t: "Koroositeh yan marih lubbittet meesii kee Qabaabako Qidenno Yallâ luk Qibaada cakkķisitaamah Yalli hebeltoh Asta kah oobise wee numtin-wellitte Yallat Agleh heenimih Sabbatah, madabaay orbeyna keenik jahannam gira, tama madab isi nafsi koroosannut yudlume marah Nabam uma madab kinni"